== Usage ==
* Wiki table header for route map template which will be transcluded in the infobox. Remember to close the route table by at least one <tt><nowiki>|}</nowiki></tt>
* Although editor can solely apply this template, in order to give the template page a tidy look, follow the syntax below:
<pre><nowiki>
<noinclude>{| {{Railway line header}}
{{bs-header}}
|-
|</noinclude>
{{BS-table3}}
<!-- *BS row templates for the structure of the route* -->
|}
<!-- *Optional notes of the ROUTE or {{tnavbar}}* -->
<noinclude>|}
<!-- *{{rdt intro|}} is suggested applying here for unified introduction to the template* -->
<!-- *More notes of the route TEMPLATE itself* -->
[[category:]]
</noinclude>
</nowiki></pre>

* The whole syntax above cannot be made into 1 template as a macro due to the paradox of functionality of <tt><nowiki><noinclude></nowiki></tt>
* See example {{tl|Sochi Light Metro route diagram}} <small>({{edit|template:Sochi Light Metro route diagram}})</small>
